sources.title: Cheyenne Tornado (1935) REB RUSSELL
sources.description:
Stars: Reb Russell, Victoria Vinton, Roger Williams
Director: Oliver Drake

A cowboy steps in when cattlemen try to force a sheepherder off the range.

metadata.Plot: Cattle man Darnell has been killed and the sheep men blamed. The Cheyenne Kid arrives and joins up with the Darnell's who are trying to drive the sheep men off the range. But he soon comes to believe the sheep men are innocent and it's not long before the real murderer is revealed and the Kid goes into action.
metadata.Actors: Reb Russell, Victoria Vinton, Roger Williams
